title: Dennis Prager July 5 Contemptible America.mp3
description:
Dennis Prager July 5, 2016

Ultimate Issues Hour: Contemptible America

Prager H3: This Fourth of July weekend, there were a spate of opinion pieces arguing how bad America is and how immoral its founding. This is no longer an exception, but a rule for the major media during the Independence Day holiday. Can America survive if its own people despise it?
